@let_it_happen
call: set_next_election_time
on-arrival: time_to_election = 3; ccf_in_government = 0; in_grand_coalition = 0; in_weimar_coalition = 0; in_popular_front = 0; ccf_toleration = 0; foreign_minister_party = "CPC"; interior_minister_party = "RPC"; justice_minister_party = "I"; labor_minister_party = "RPC"; reichswehr_minister_party = "I"; economic_minister_party = lpc_name; finance_minister_party = "CPC"; agriculture_minister_party = "RPC"; labor_minister = "Stegerwald"; interior_minister = "Wirth"; finance_minister = "Moldenhauer"; economic_minister = "Curtius"; justice_minister = "Koch-Weser"; foreign_minister = "Stresemann"; agriculture_minister = "Dietrich"; reichswehr_minister = "Groener";  coalition_dissent = 0; pro_republic -= 5; old_middle_ccf -= 3; new_middle_ccf -= 2; workers_ccf -= 3 if pro_republic < 50; workers_ccf -= 4 if pro_republic < 40; old_middle_nsdap += 4 if pro_republic < 50; new_middle_nsdap += 3 if pro_republic < 50
go-to: let_it_happen_georgev if monarch != "Woodsworth"; let_it_happen_woodsworth if monarch == "Woodsworth"

@let_it_happen_georgev
on-arrival: prime_minister = "Brüning"; prime_minister_party = "RPC"; welfare -= 2;

The vote succeeds, and our government has resigned. Prime Minister Brüning has been appointed as the head of an acting government, consisting solely of the bourgeois parties. He immediately proceeds to cut welfare spending substantially.

New elections have been set for [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +].

@let_it_happen_woodsworth
on-arrival: ccf_caretaker = 1

The vote succeeds, and our government has resigned. Prime Minister [+ prime_minister +] remains as the head of a caretaker government, but no longer has the power to enact new policies.

New elections have been set for [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +].
